Git-commit: 3a7f2f6a9e43f2c5ce45d4ca19c43bf61df3f0dd
Patch-mainline: v3.6-rc1

Zero initialize the mode_cmd structure when creating the kernel
framebuffer. Avoids having uninitialized data in offsets[0] for
instance.

